= API Stability =
There is no API version number and no even non-binding guarantees about API stability are being made.

For example for the VirtualBox stable version number {{project name long}}, [[Template:VersionNew]] was used earlier anyhow prior any request for any API functions has been made. Making that version information available through an easy to parse way is pretty simple thanks to mediawiki index.php already built-in function action=raw.

= API Completeness =
Other information might be already available (since the wiki or forum software has these features anyhow). Please ask in forums.

